data.description: Charming 1940s Stone Home on a Corner Lot in the Highly Desirable Oak Ridge Drive Neighborhood!  Welcome to this classic beauty, boasting 2013 sqft of living space with 4 bedrooms and 1.5 bathrooms, plus an additional 500 sqft of unfinished basement, perfect for storage or future expansion possibilities. This prime location on Oak Ridge Drive is a treasure trove for garage sale enthusiasts, offering the ideal spot for hosting and exploring neighborhood sales. Step inside and you'll be greeted by original fixtures that have been thoughtfully blended with modern touches, giving this home a unique character that's both timeless and contemporary. The updated granite counters in the kitchen add a touch of luxury, and the adorable breakfast nook One of the bedrooms is ideally suited for a nursery or home office, and you'll be charmed by the glass double doors that welcome you into another cozy bedroom. The whitewashed fireplace adds character and warmth to the living space, complementing the original wood floors that exude a sense of history. Step outside onto the beautiful stone back patio and envision the endless possibilities for outdoor gatherings, BBQs, or simply relaxing. Don't miss your chance to own this delightful piece of Neosho history. With its timeless appeal and modern comforts, this home is a rare find. Schedule a showing today and make it your own!
